Kũgaathĩrĩria ũhootani


1  MWATHANI, mũthamaki nĩakeneetio nĩ we nĩ ũndũ nĩũmũheete hinya;

nĩ mũcanjamũku nĩ ũndũ nĩũmũhootanĩire.


2  Nĩũmũhingĩirie ũrĩa erirĩirie na ngoro yake,

na ndwagĩĩte kũmũcookeria ũrĩa akũhoeete na mĩromo yake.


3  Nĩũmũreehithĩirie iraathimo nene,

na ũkamwĩkĩra mũtwe thũmbĩ ya thahabu ĩrĩa njega mũno.


4  Aakũhoire muoyo, nawe ũkĩmũhe,

ũgĩkĩmuongerera matukũ maingĩ.


5  Riiri wake nĩ mũnene nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa wee ũmũteithĩĩtie;

nĩũmũheete ũnene o na igweta.


6  Nĩũmũraathimĩĩte na iraathimo cia gũtũũra nginya tene na tene,

na ũgatũma aikarage akeneete nĩ ũndũ wa gũkuonaga.


7  Nĩ gũkorwo mũthamaki ehokeete o MWATHANI

na tondũ wa ũtugi wa Ũrĩa Ũrĩ Igũrũ Mũno ndarĩ hingo akeenyenyeka.


8  Guoko gwaku nĩgũkaanyiita thũ ciaku ciothe;

guoko gwaku kwa ũrĩo nĩgũgaakumbata arĩa oothe magũthũire.


9  Rĩrĩa ũkaamoimĩrĩra-rĩ, ũkaamaniina mahaane o ta macinĩĩtwo na mwaki mũnene.

Nĩkũmeria ũkaamameria nĩ ũrĩa ũmaraakarĩire MWATHANI

naguo mwaki ũmaniine.


10  Nĩũkaaniina ciana ciao ciothe ciehere gũũkũ thĩ;

mbeũ yao ĩthire biũ thĩinĩ wa andũ.


11  O na mangĩbanga ũrĩa megũgwĩka ũũru,

matingĩgĩa na ũhootani mĩbangoinĩ ĩyo yao ya ungumania.


12  Nĩ gũkorwo wee nĩũkaamaratha na mĩguĩ yaku,

o nginya mahũndũke moore.


13  Nĩtũgũgũkumia, MWATHANI, nĩ ũndũ wa hinya waku mũnene,

o na tũine na tũgaathe ũhoti waku.

